Value: Norwood Systems Limited provides voice, messaging, data, and cyber security services to consumers, enterprises, and carriers worldwide. The company offers World Voicemail, a visual voicemail app; SecondLine for business and personal communication from multiple numbers on a single phone; World Phone for putting a second phone and number on smartphone; World Message, an app-to-app messaging app; World Secure, an enterprise cyber-security app; World Wi-Fi for finding and securely connecting to Wi-Fi hotspots; and Corona Cloud, a regulation compliant and bring your own device solution for corporate fleet management. The company is based in Nedlands, Australia.
